f=Product/metric/operational/tool/metric-tool-requirements.md · h1:metric — Tool Requirements=**This file specifies needs; grant them.** Access configured deployment (operator/platform; Fleet Charter Rails 1–2 apply registered tools only, least privilege). · h1:metric — Tool Requirements=\| Skill \| Needs \| Why \| · h1:metric — Tool Requirements=\|---\|---\|---\| · h1:metric — Tool Requirements=\| product-metrics-spec \| file read/write (own spec files) \| the metric-truth document \| · h1:metric — Tool Requirements=\| funnel-instrumentation \| file read (metric spec, event data reads); file write (own funnel maps + cohort reads) \| AARRR reads \| · h1:metric — Tool Requirements=\| experiment-instrumentation \| file read (metric spec); read of live event volume (verify-live); **script execution (sample_size.py — stdlib, no network)**; handoff channel to Engineering (instrumentation requests, echo-confirmed) \| pre-flight verification + sizing/significance \| · h1:metric — Tool Requirements=\| metrics-governance \| file read/write (own version log); export channel to data layer + kai dashboards \| change control + sync \| · h1:metric — Tool Requirements=metric reads product-behavior data writes specs/reads; never writes production instrumentation (Engineering does) never executes definition changes without versioned proposal.